<p>
  <span class="nym">Adaly</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Uncertain. Possibly related to <a class="nym" href="Alice">Alice</a> or <a class="nym" href="Adeline">Adeline</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Our sole example of the name, from <span class="bib"><span class="key">SDHK</span> <span class="loc">no. 10938</span></span>, contains a footnote indicating that the SDHK editors have not previously come across this name, and that it may be a derivative of either <i>Adeliza</i> or <i>Adhelin</i>, Swedish forms of <a class="nym" href="Alice">Alice</a> and <a class="nym" href="Adeline">Adeline</a>, respectively.</p>
  
  


